column10: The triple species hybrid (G. hirsutum Oeltapine 14 x G. longicalyx)2 x Gossypium armourianum Kearny (HLA) was crossed and backcrossed for seven generations into G. hirsutum cultivars and single plants were selected for reniform resistance and yield after each generation.
